Simple feed aggregator + search, focusing on developer / academic blogs.

A database for your entries will be created in db/aggir.db at initial launch.

Requirements :

rfeedparser ( http://github.com/jmhodges/rfeedparser/tree/master )
Sequel ( http://sequel.rubyforge.org )
SQLite3 ( http://www.sqlite.org/ )
Solr ( http://lucene.apache.org/solr/ )

For Testing:
Shoulda ( http://thoughtbot.com/projects/shoulda )
FlexMock